FBIS3-32121 "drlat022_m_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 Brazil Bishops Chairman Endorses Tax Increase in Economic Plan PY0102223794 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 2100 GMT 1 Feb 94 PY0102223794 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] Bishop Luciano Mendes de Almeida, chairman of the National Conference of Brazilian Bishops [CNBB], defends the tax increase foreseen in the government economic plan. Bishop Mendes said this measure is necessary to guarantee resources for national social programs. The CNBB chairman considers Congress' decision not to increase the taxes paid by large companies an injustice.
